description: The Alice Collection by MJL Furniture Designs is a collection of stunning, lavish headboards featuring flawless design and magnificent craftsmanship. The Alice full size headboard measures 55"W x 2"D x 26"H and weighs 24 lbs. Upon delivery of headboard some assembly is required. The full headboards are expertly constructed using the most resilient and enduring woods. The wood full headboard is then carefully upholstered with the softest, most luxurious cotton. An endless variety of utterly alluring color and pattern combinations are available to adorn this upholstered headboard. MJL Furniture Designs crafts and designs luxurious furniture using the finest, most resilient woods and soft, elegant fabrics. A combined 45 years of expertise, talent and experience ensures the impeccable and flawless nature of every MJL product. Every piece is proudly conceived, designed and manufactured in California, U.S.A.
